{
  "stem": "1826.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she has such a special feeling for me, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But how-- what shall we do with other guy, you know-- with the other guy?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he had some relatives in a town about 40 miles from Krzemieniec, from this city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she managed to find a guy how-- who lived somehow on the same direction.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he took him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He went with him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he hoped to reach the other town, where he had relatives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he-- then I was the only one there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Maria ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nikichna ?] had to bring me food-- twice a day, whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the neighbors, from the windows, I suppose, they saw something suspicious that she-- that repeats itself every day-- you know, every day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then I suppose they denounced her to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one day, I was lying on this-- on the attic, you know, in the hay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I hear the German language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I look through the-- you know, the-- [? haystack. ?] And I see two German gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I didn't know what to do with myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was in the hay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I was sleeping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I somehow tried to-- to mix up a little bit the hay, you know, so it won't [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But underneath there, was a woman who brought some-- some grain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were not supposed to do it-- against the law.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So she came here, from the village, with the-- with the, you know, the grain.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she was on the main floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I was on the attic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when the Germans started to walk up a ladder to the attic, I jumped down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She didn't hear me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She didn't hear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Now, we come into a situation that is-- you can-- logic fails.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
